{
  "stem": "15962.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Not to be too tall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Not to be too small.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Not to be too slow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Not to be too fast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Not to have any color.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "To be just blend into the background.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that became particularly important later on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Not to be selected.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Not-- if some-- a German came and said, who can-- who has a nice handwriting and wants to-- to help us paint or something like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Inevitably, those people were selected for some hard labor or clean toilets or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there were many choices that later on one had to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Is should you go right, should you go left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Should you stand with this crowd.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Should you stand with another.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the manner of survival was complete series of coincidences and luck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I don't believe that only the strong survived, or only the smart survived, or-- or only the strong or half-witted survived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The-- this-- there were so many events, at least in my life, which were purely coincidental.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's more a-- a feeling that I have now than going back and recalling specific events.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] there was another transport that came from Terezin in May of 1944.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that transport also came to our camp to take the place of the 5,000 that was gassed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were once again completely full.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this did not last very long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Almost to the day six months after we arrived, or close to that period, there were rumors that the camp is being liquidated.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were very much afraid that we will all be gassed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then the order came that all the men that were capable of hard work should report for selection.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
